{"id":"shunammite","term":"Shunammite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A person of Shunem (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 1:3\">1 Kings 1:3</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 4:12\">2 Kings 4:12</a>). The Syr. and Arab. read “Sulamite.”</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Kings 1:3","2 Kings 4:12"]}